Text_Info_InformationPanel_TopPanel_Body:
This game is in its early stages of development. 

While we work on getting all Space Station 13 features in eventually, most are not in yet, and some are jerry-rigged.

So keep in mind that this game does not yet represent SS13 in current state, and be warned of bugs you're likely to encounter!
